original_title: Supermatch 3: The Sadist and The Muscleboy
overview: Easily among the most popular titles in the Can-Am erota-wrestling video library are our totally original storyline SUPERMATCHES. Best selling SUPERMATCHES 1 & 2 were FLEX VS DOUG BRANDON, and KICKASS BODYBUILDER FEUD. SUPERMATCH 3 pits 21 year old muscleboy Tony Valor against the brutally sadistic Doug Brandon in a grueling one hour, four part, pro action, bare assed epic (all on the same DVD).
title: Supermatch 3: The Sadist and The Muscleboy
